description: Meggrolls are whatever you crave wrapped in a hot and crispy edible package.What are you in the mood for?Crave a little Tex-Mex?Maybe today you want to travel to the Mediterranean.I know what you want! Just a good burger, right?All of these flavors and more are available in these little crispy rolls. And for dessert, check out the apple pie, s'mores, or even Boston cream pie!On a DC street near you!
name: Meggrolls
